text: Mohamed Ould Cheikh Mohamed Ahmed Ould Ghazouani (; born 4 December 1956), also known as Ghazouani and Ould Ghazouani, is a Mauritanian politician and retired Mauritanian Army general. He is the President of Mauritania, since 1 August 2019. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Mauritanian generals Category:Presidents of Mauritania Category:Current national leaders
